  <brief_title>Effects of Drainage in Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>To Drain or Not to Drain in Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy for the Patients With Acutely Inflamed Gallbladder ; a Multicenter Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
